	<TextEquiv>
	<Unicode>blog she began a year ago, Broadway &amp;
Me (broadwayandme.blogspot.com). The
one consolation for us and for the readers
of TIME is that Ian will continue to con-
tribute to the magazine as a writer and
an editor. It is ﬁtting that we pay tribute
